Founded in 2021, Kodifly is a fast-growing start-up backed by the Nvidia Inception, HKSTP’s Incubation, HKAI Lab accelerator and HKU Deeptech 100. We strive to accelerate smart city transformation with mobility and transportation A.I. including AIoT systems integration, video and LiDAR analytics solutions.




